Run the Sparrow gRPC service

Usage: sparrow-main serve [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --service-addr <SERVICE_ADDR>
          Address to run the service on
          
          [env: SPARROW_GRPC_ADDR=]
          [default: 0.0.0.0:50052]

      --flight-record-path <FLIGHT_RECORD_PATH>
          Path for writing (flight records and query plans).
          
          If `None`, flight records and query plans will not be written.
          
          For example, `s3://<bucket>/flight_records` to write to the `flight_records` prefix of the given S3 bucket.
          
          [env: SPARROW_FLIGHT_RECORD_PATH=]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

  -V, --version
          Print version

